你能够调用以下的API:
[['ArtActivityTracker.get_current_habits', {'name': 'ArtActivityTracker.get_current_habits', 'description': 'Retrieve the current art activity habits of the user.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'habits', 'description': 'A list of current art activities including painting, sculpting, and photography.'}]}], ['RetirementPlanner.get_retirement_age', {'name': 'RetirementPlanner.get_retirement_age', 'description': 'Get the estimated retirement age of the user.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'retirementAge', 'description': 'The estimated retirement age.'}]}], ['ArtActivityCostAnalyzer.get_cost_and_return', {'name': 'ArtActivityCostAnalyzer.get_cost_and_return', 'description': 'Analyze the cost and return rate of different art activities.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'activity', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of art activity.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'cost', 'description': 'The cost of the activity.'}, {'name': 'returnRate', 'description': 'The return rate of the activity.'}]}], ['LocalGovernment.get_art_subsidy_policy', {'name': 'LocalGovernment.get_art_subsidy_policy', 'description': 'Retrieve the art subsidy policy of a specific region.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'region', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The region for which the policy is to be retrieved.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'subsidyPolicy', 'description': 'The subsidy policy for art activities in the region.'}]}], ['BudgetPlanner.create_art_activity_budget', {'name': 'BudgetPlanner.create_art_activity_budget', 'description': 'Create a budget for retirement art activities based on current habits, cost, return rate, and subsidy policy.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'retirementAge', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The estimated retirement age.'}, {'name': 'currentHabits', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The current art activity habits.'}, {'name': 'costAndReturn', 'type': 'LIST', 'description': 'A list of cost and return rate for each activity.'}, {'name': 'subsidyPolicy', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The subsidy policy for art activities.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'budget', 'description': 'The budget for retirement art activities.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
